skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: bucktooth village
des: This is a memory game set in a fictional rabbit town called Bucktooth Village. You need to help retrieve the carrots that were scattered in the nearby labyrinth by a mischievous white rabbit. You can travel up, down, left, or right in the labyrinth. You are given one direction at a time, and must repeat ALL the directions given in order to collect the carrot. How many carrots can you bring back?
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
